Telenor CEO ‘Pleased’ With New VimpelCom Management Statements

-- B y   M e e r a   B h a t i a
-- 
2011-09-22T07:52:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/telenor-revises-dividend-policy-sees-opex-sales-below-35-in-13.html
Telenor ASA (TEL) ’s Chief Executive
Officer Jon Fredrik Baksaas said he’s positive to the changes
that have been made in Vimpelcom’s management.  The Fornebu-based company is “pleased” with statements
from the new VimpelCom management and its focus on “operational
improvements,” the executive said during the company’s capital
markets day today. Telenor said it expects “value creation”
from VimpelCom and added that the arbitration process is
ongoing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Meera Bhatia at 
 mbhatia2@bloomberg.net  